#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:108
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[1]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CABAL ROOMS:\n"
"This enemy has one or more Cabal rooms, marked by the unique pink symbols and C icon in the top left. Cabal rooms will take no hull damage from weapons. Fires and breaches in the rooms will also be instantly fixed. Cabal rooms will take system damage as normal."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:113
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[2]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CABAL'S PROTECTION ARRAY:\n"
"This enemy's crew will passively heal anywhere on their ship so long as their Medbay is powered, at 100% speed of the current Medbay power level.\n"
"\n"
"Their crew will also have 25% more movement speed per medbay level powered. Their Totality Commanders will also gain an extra charge of their full health healing for as long as their medbay has 3 or more power in it."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:120
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[3]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"EXTERMINATOR'S AETHER SHIELD:\n"
"This enemy is protected by a massive sophisticated and resilient Energy Shield. In addition to the usual Super Shield benefits, shields also recharge 25% faster."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:125
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[4]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"TINFOIL ARRAY:\n"
"While enemy Mind Control is powered to lvl 3, all enemy crew gain complete MC immunity."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:130
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[5]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"COMMONWEALTH MAINTENANCE INFRASTRUCTURE:\n"
"This enemy ship is filled with incredibly advanced web of nanomachine-spewing nodes which will passively damage your crew for 5 hp/s and heal 5 hp/s to enemy drones and metallic crew. Actively puts out fires and repairs breaches on the enemy ship."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:135
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[6]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"LIGHTWEIGHT COMMONWEALTH MAINTENANCE INFRASTRUCTURE:\n"
"This enemy ship is filled with incredibly advanced web of nanomachine-spewing nodes which will passively damage your crew for 2.5 hp/s and heal 2.5 hp/s to enemy drones and metallic crew. Actively puts out fires and repairs breaches on the enemy ship."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:140
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[7]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"DAMAGED WEAPONS:\n"
"This enemy's weapon system has been heavily damaged, it will take 50% longer to charge."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:145
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[8]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"BONUS REVENANT LOOT:\n"
"This enemy is carrying a special preternaturally-enhanced weapon or drone. Destroying the vessel only has a 50% chance to drop the item, but killing the crew will guarantee it drops.\n"
"\n"
"The first time you obtain the loot weapon, you will also unlock a ship.\n"
"\n"
"If the ship is an automated vessel, the loot will always drop."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:154
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[9]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"REVENANT LOOT:\n"
"This enemy is carrying a special preternaturally-enhanced weapon or drone. Destroying the vessel only has a 50% chance to drop the item, but killing the crew will guarantee it drops.\n"
"\n"
"If the ship is an automated vessel, the loot will always drop."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:161
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[10]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"FLAGSHIP LOOT:\n"
"This enemy is carrying a special preternaturally-enhanced weapon or drone. Destroying the vessel or killing the crew will guarantee it drops."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:166
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[11]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"REVENANT THREAT:\n"
"This enemy will pose a major threat to an unprepared vessel. The dark energies it emits prevent your FTL Drive from charging, so you will have to use everything you've got to win!"

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:171
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[12]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CHAOTIC REVENANT THREAT:\n"
"There's no escape now, Renegade.\n"
"\t/\n"
":)"

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:178
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[13]/tooltip"
msgstr "Rest now."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:182
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[14]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CURSED ROOMS:\n"
"This enemy has one or more cursed rooms, marked by the pink border. Cursed rooms are immune to system and ion damage, and are sabotaged at half speed. These rooms take fire and hull damage as normal."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:187
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[15]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CORRUPTED ROOMS:\n"
"This enemy has one or more corrupted rooms, marked by rapidly flashing colors. Corrupted rooms are immune to system and ion damage, are sabotaged at a tenth of the normal speed, and deal 100 hp/s in damage to your crew. Enemy crew are healed for 100 hp/s in these rooms."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:192
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[16]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"BREACH SEALANT:\n"
"Breaches on the enemy ship will automatically be repaired even in the absence of crew."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:197
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[17]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"ANCIENT HYPER-IGNITER:\n"
"This enemy's weapons start charged, and they will all fire as soon as the fight starts. Additionally, their weapons charge 15% faster."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:202
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[18]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"XENOPHOBIA:\n"
"This enemy's human crew will gain a 33% buff to all main stats, but their non-human crew have a 40% loss to all main stats.\n"
"(Main stats include health, damage, repair, sabotage, and movement speed)."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:208
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[19]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"NEW ORDER:\n"
"This enemy's Zoltan crew provide 1 extra power, can teleport to any room on either ship, and have 1.5x repair speed and combat damage, but their non-Zoltan crew have a 40% loss to all main stats.\n"
"(Main stats include health, damage, repair, sabotage, and movement speed)."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:214
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[20]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"DENSER MOLECULES:\n"
"This ship's Ghost crew have 20 extra health, but they can't phase through doors."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:219
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[21]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CHEMICAL PROLIFERATION:\n"
"This ship's Ghost crew passively heal from fire. Gouls heal from this at halved speed."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:224
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[22]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"HULKING MASS:\n"
"This ship's Morph crew have 50% extra health, but move at half speed."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:229
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[23]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"COMBAT SYSTEMS:\n"
"This ship's Engi crew have standard combat damage and 10 extra health, but lose 25% of their repair speed."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:234
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[24]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"HEKTAR ULTRA-STICK GEL(tm):\n"
"Enemy crew on their ship are stunned for half the usual duration. In this ship's empty rooms, enemies take halved damage from all sources, and your crew move 20% slower."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:239
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[25]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"ENVIRONMENTAL ADAPTATION:\n"
"This ship's Engi crew are immune to suffocation."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:244
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[26]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CRYSTALLIZED HYDROGEN:\n"
"This ship's Crystal crew are immune to suffocation."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:249
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[27]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"COMMONWEALTH ENERGY SHIELD:\n"
"This enemy is protected by an advanced energy shield which also has a 50% chance to negate ion damage."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:254
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[28]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"COMMONWEALTH AETHER FORGE:\n"
"Although the primary purpose of this vessel's forge is to make new weapons, it also runs a basic defense system that deals 3 hp/s in damage to your crew if they board the ship."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:259
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[29]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CEREBRAL OVERCHARGE:\n"
"Enemy crew gain a 15% buff to repair and combat damage, and heal 50% faster while their Mind Control system is powered."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:264
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[30]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"PERFECTED INTERNALS:\n"
"This enemy's systems are highly optimized, boasting a number of special bonuses.\n"
"- 5% faster weapon charge.\n"
"- 10% faster shield charge.\n"
"- 15% faster FTL Drive charge.\n"
"- 15% hull resist chance, 15% system resist chance, and 50% ion resist chance.\n"
"- Friendly crew and drones in your ship constantly heal 3 hp/s.\n"
"- Enemy crew and drones in your ship constantly take 5 hp/s in damage."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:275
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[31]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"PECULIAR SHIELDING:\n"
"This enemy is protected by an advanced energy shield which also prevents your crew from using short-range teleporters while inside the enemy ship."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:280
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[32]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"ECTOPLASMIC GEL:\n"
"Breaches on the enemy ship will automatically be repaired instantly even in the absence of crew. In this ship's empty rooms, enemy crew are immune to hazards, and your crew move at half speed and lose the ability to fight."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:285
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[33]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"IONIZED NEBULA GAS:\n"
"Enemy crew on this ship are immune to being stunned, and the ship itself is immune to ion damage. Your crew will take damage over time while boarding, and drones take double damage."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:290
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[34]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"GHOSTLY PHEROMONES:\n"
"The enemy ship gains increasingly strong bonuses to crew for each powered level of Life Support.\n"
"- 1 power: Friendly crew gain immunity to suffocation.\n"
"- 2 power: Friendly crew gain the ability to phase through doors.\n"
"- 3 power: Friendly crew gain the ability to teleport to any room on your ship.\n"
"- 4 power: Friendly crew gain the ability to teleport to any room and to either ship directly."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:299
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[35]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CURSED PHEROMONES:\n"
"The enemy ship gains increasingly strong bonuses to crew for each powered level of Life Support.\n"
"- 1 power: Friendly crew gain immunity to all hazards.\n"
"- 2 power: Friendly crew gain 20% extra sabotage speed and the ability to phase through doors.\n"
"- 3 power: Friendly crew gain 20% extra health and the ability to teleport to any room on your ship.\n"
"- 4 power: Friendly crew gain 20% extra combat damage and the ability to teleport to any room and to either ship directly."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:308
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[36]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"MOLTEN ARMOR:\n"
"Your crew on this ship passively take 15 hp/s in damage. This damage counts as fire damage, and is modified accordingly. The ship also has a 25% chance to negate any hull damage, impacts that deal 1 damage have a 20% chance to be negated, and all other damage is reduced by 1."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:313
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[37]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"ENERGY SIPHON:\n"
"\tFor each crew drone the enemy control, their crew gains +0.25x damage and repair as well as +25 max health. Drones fired by their weapons and artilleries also count towards this number."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:318
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[38]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"EMERGENCY AUTOPILOT:\n"
"This ship has a sophisticated form of autopilot which will keep it fully functional and working for as long as there is at least a single enemy alive or in the process of being cloned."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:323
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[39]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"HOLY CONVICTION:\n"
"Enemy crew heal and are cloned 50% faster, and the enemy ship's beam weapons pierce 2 additional shield layers."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:328
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[40]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"MAGICAL SHIELD:\n"
"An absurdly powerful energy shield protecting G's ship. Has an integrity of 80 hitpoints."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:333
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[41]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CURSED SHIELD:\n"
"An absurdly powerful energy shield protecting G's ship. Has an integrity of 80 hitpoints, and gives the enemy ship a 50% chance to resist ion damage."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:338
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[42]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"NECROMANTIC AURA:\n"
"The enemy's Specter crew have 100 more health and resist mind control."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:343
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[43]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"AETHER NECRONOMICON:\n"
"Enemy crew will be revived as Specters after dying; this does not interrupt standard cloning processes. Specters can't be revived."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:348
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[44]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"Frozen ARMOR:\n"
"Every time you deal hull damage to this enemy with your weapons, a shard will break off and fly towards your ship. It will pierce 2 shields and can't be shot down by defense drones, deals 1 damage and locks down rooms on hit. The ship also has a 50% chance to negate system damage."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:353
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[45]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"DEATHLY SPORES:\n"
"Your crew will be infected with deathly spores, causing any allied crew who dies to make other allied crew take 10% more damage and increases their active ability cooldowns by 10%. This effect stacks and applies across all ships\n"
"\n"
"Effect is removed on jump."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:360
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[46]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"FRIGID AIR:\n"
"The enemy's Snowman crew heal for 20 hp/s while inside the enemy ship."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:365
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[47]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"LIVING SHIP:\n"
"This enemy ship is alive, and has consumed one or more of its old crewmates. The augments it has acquired from this process have their icons displayed."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:370
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[48]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"SPECTRAL NANOMACHINES:\n"
"This enemy will automatically repair all of its systems at the speed of a human, multiplied by the amount of power in its Drone Control."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:375
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[49]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"SHIELD ADAPTER:\n"
"This enemy can naturally generate layers of energy shielding. The regeneration rate and maximum number of layers is dependent on the strength of their Shields, and they regenerate regular shielding at half the rate."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:380
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[50]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"ANNIHILATION GRID:\n"
"Your crew on this ship lose 10 hp/s, lose the ability to phase through doors or move by teleporting, and deal halved damage to doors."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:385
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[51]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"SELF AWARE COGNITIVE INTELLIGENCE:\n"
"This enemy is automated, and all of their systems are automatically manned at level 2 skill."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:390
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[52]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"HARD-LIGHT HULL:\n"
"This ship's hull health is always equal to the integrity of its energy shield."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:395
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[53]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"ZOLTAN ENERGY GRID:\n"
"Your crew on this ship lose 4 hp/s, plus an extra 2 hp/s for every level of Door Control it has beyond the first. If they die, they fully repair the system they are standing in, overwriting any other death effect they may have."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:400
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[54]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"FIELD OF STATIC:\n"
"This ship's rooms are protected by some kind of mysterious static energy. Your crew onboard this ship will be frozen in place, entranced by its horrifying interior until removed from the ship."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:405
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[55]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"WATCHER'S PROTECTION:\n"
"This enemy is protected by an energy shield infused with esoteric, powerful chaos. It has an integrity of 15 hit points, doubles as a hard-light bypass unit that cannot be counteracted, and grants this ship a 50% chance to take no damage from non-ion damage."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:410
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[56]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"LEGIONNAIRE'S AEGIS:\n"
"This enemy is protected by a highly resilient energy shield. It has an integrity of 10 hit points. While the energy shield is up:\n"
"\n"
"- The fire rate of the enemy's Weapons and Artillery is improved by 20%;\n"
"- The enemy's ship's evasion is increased by 10;"

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:418
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[57]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"SPIRIT OF THE REBELLION:\n"
"This enemy's Human crew are considered to have all three of their basic lab upgrades."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:423
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[58]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"R.U.E.S. ROYAL PLATING:\n"
"This ship's unique hull armor provides several bonuses.\n"
"- 20% hull resist chance. Impacts that deal 1 damage have a 40% chance to be negated, and all other damage is reduced by 1.\n"
"- Breaches on this enemy will automatically be repaired even in the absence of crew.\n"
"- Provides a 35% crew combat resistance and a 50% hazard resistance to enemy crew in empty rooms.\n"
"- For each active power bar in Life Support, their crew get a bonus 25% movement speed, 6.25% maximum health, and reduces active ability cooldowns by 15%."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:432
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[59]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"GILDED SYSTEMS:\n"
"This ship's systems become more efficient the more scrap it carries. Every 10 scrap, its weapons charge 1% faster. Every 5 scrap, its shields regenerate 1% faster."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:437
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[60]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"SCRAP HOARD:\n"
"This ship carries 100 scrap in its cargo bay."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:442
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[61]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"SPIDER INFESTATION:\n"
"Every 25 seconds, a hostile spider will violently burst out of all of your crew. This spider will live for 5 seconds, and deals 0.5x combat damage."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:447
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[62]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CLOAK OF DARKNESS:\n"
"Your projectiles have a 25% chance to have no effect against this ship."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:452
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[4]/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:shipIcon[63]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"FORBIDDEN DESIGN:\n"
